cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper is focused on analyzing deep neural networks for image recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the computational complexity and memory usage of the networks, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves experimentation and analysis of performance indices, which could fall under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
